#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:333
msgid "8.1 累计收益与归一化（`cum_return` / `normalize`）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:335
msgid ""
"返回 **新** ``HistoryPanel``（不修改原面板），默认对解析后的 ``close`` 列计算；输出列名为 "
